## text

### Source (en)

~~~text
Can the volume of data be accommodated by the standard network connection? Has a special network connection (e.g. light path) that is needed been reserved?
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
現有的標準網路連線是否足以容納此資料量？是否已預留所需的特殊網路連線（例如：光通道網路）？
~~~
